    "In addition, as the concept of the metaverse becomes more widely known in 2022, more keywords begin to appear from different fields, such as 5G, streaming media, system, integration, and green.",
    "But most of these words are short-lived in a period of rapid development.Several significant limitations require consideration in this investigation.",
    "The methodological approach has some limitations as it only utilizes the WOS database, potentially leading to the exclusion of essential sources from other databases, such as Dimensions, Scopus, CORE, CiteSeerX and so on.",
    "Consequently, research findings related to metaverses may have been overlooked.",
    "Moreover, the bibliometric analysis in this paper was conducted in Dec 2023."
